{"tid":2292710,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過蔬菜汁斷食法？","createTime":"2020-11-19T16:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T16:48:08.000Z","uid":343770,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"19ac119ca2d7b809a98b231c4b1429fade8a9f84","tid":2292710,"uid":343770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JbC4Cye7s7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJbC4Cye7s7k&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=d57c1e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JbC4Cye7s7k</a><br />\n<br />\n近排開始研究減肥。試過168斷食，兩個月內令我從62kg左右減到57kg左右。減到57開始一個月無減過，每日一小時做運動（跑步5km）+晚黑唔食澱粉，都減唔到。已經少食甜野（一個禮拜2次甜野）。<br />\n<br />\n於是開始上網搵關於蔬果汁斷食嘅資料，好似都幾有效，但係唔知我呢d小基數減肥得唔得？ 利申：162cm，57kg，想減到50kg。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主要係下半身太肥。再利申我唔驚減到無波，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我有小小怕斷M<br />\n<br />\n想知有無人試過，有無用？"},{"pid":"5a68382ed3ca26154fe4e36bd84e96ceb9345d1f","tid":2292710,"uid":315852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊work唔work，但完全唔食其他野我真係寧願死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b33d085d306bd4ae352195007a0a6452ba6025d","tid":2292710,"uid":89546,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"又想減肥又唔計marco又要食甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bb50a24a5cca07ded2bf9495ae8dd0ea07252a","tid":2292710,"uid":247737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"想減特定部位嘅話唔work"},{"pid":"e39d4e226c04e23b341b9efd4e8062c8e9a7681a","tid":2292710,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"01cc3ed620b1d85ac5d6ac1f633debd62ad061e9","tid":2292710,"uid":231089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:46:19.000